This is shaped like a -- or
designed like an actual bus ticket

00:14:23.660 --> 00:14:25.200
if you're used to riding in Muni.

00:14:25.540 --> 00:14:26.910
Really effective colors.

00:14:26.920 --> 00:14:29.300
You know, alludes to what it's doing.

00:14:29.300 --> 00:14:31.030
Really love this app icon.

00:14:31.230 --> 00:14:32.120
Here's Hipstamatics.

00:14:32.230 --> 00:14:33.890
This is a famous app icon.

00:14:33.900 --> 00:14:38.130
They're mimicking the actual toy
