00:19:46.870 --> 00:19:48.700
And it really worked well.

00:19:48.700 --> 00:19:49.700
And that's where they finally landed.

00:19:49.700 --> 00:19:51.700
And I think it turned out really nicely.

00:19:51.700 --> 00:19:55.700
If you look at this icon up close,
