00:55:03.110 --> 00:55:05.640
It's used, it's printed up,
it's bookmarked.

00:55:05.640 --> 00:55:09.330
And it's actually very reminiscent of
the HIG that you would see if you're

00:55:09.330 --> 00:55:11.980
walking around the offices in Cupertino.

